{"id":"808259565165658112","type":"text","timestamp":1770816388,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/808259565165658112","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":["shitposting","shitpost","meme","memes","retro meme","retro memes","transgender","sapphic","wlw","lgbtq","gay","mtf","transbian","lgbtqia","sapphic blog","tumblr classic"],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a href=\"https://tehnakki.tumblr.com/post/176971103100/lilyrose225writes-psychicmayhem\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">tehnakki</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a href=\"https://lilyrose225writes.tumblr.com/post/173749849623/psychicmayhem-just-shower-thoughts-earth-is\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">lilyrose225writes</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://psychicmayhem.tumblr.com/post/172120731861/just-shower-thoughts-earth-is-currently-at-the\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">psychicmayhem</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://just-shower-thoughts.tumblr.com/post/172118754959/earth-is-currently-at-the-stage-that-leads-into\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">just-shower-thoughts</a>:</p>\n<blockquote><p>Earth is currently at the stage that leads into either Star Trek, or Mad Max.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Astute observers will recall that in <i>Star Trek</i>, Earth was <i>Mad Max</i> for several years before becoming <i>Star Trek</i>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>i feel a sudden bloom of hope inside me</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>This is the most hopefully thing I’ve read this week</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"just-shower-thoughts"},"post":{"id":"172118754959"}},{"blog":{"name":"psychicmayhem"},"post":{"id":"172120731861"}},{"blog":{"name":"lilyrose225writes"},"post":{"id":"173749849623"}},{"blog":{"name":"tehnakki"},"post":{"id":"176971103100"}}],"baseline_notes":28091,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}